    howToGetThere: "From Pokhara Lakeside, taxis take 30\u201335 minutes (NPR 800\u20131200 one-way). Shared jeeps depart from Lakeside around 4:30 AM for sunrise visits (NPR 300\u2013400 per seat). The hiking trail ascends from Miruwa village on the Pokhara-Baglung Highway (1.5\u20132 hours) or from Lakeside via Kaskikot (2\u20133 hours). Most paragliding operators include taxi transfers in the package price.",
